descriptionMarkdown:
You will need to load up the blueprint chest with a blueprint book with the recipes to use.
The slots of the book need to match the configuration on the constant combinator with "NIL" in it. Items are to have values corresponding to their slot in the blueprint book.

Have a cannon with no recipe set in the first slot, the rest matching the number of the material the constant combinator is set to.

Use the push button to clear out the accumulator combinator logic when restarting the fCPU.

Send the requests from the remote base into the combinator pointed to by the arrow.

Mods: Space Exploration modpack + fCPU for SE + Push Button


Example Blueprint Book:


title: Multi-Delivery Cannon
